        <p class="GiftBox-lbl">Contrepoints <strong>ne peut exister sans vos dons</strong></p>
        <p class="GiftBox-btnBar"><a class="GiftBox-btn" href="https://www.contrepoints.org/aider-contrepoints">FAIRE UN DON</a></p>
